description:
Vendetta is back and schooling newcomer Samantha Sin. Samantha used to be a gymnast, she is fit, flexible, and she contacted US to wrestle. Samantha shows great promise as an upcoming ranked contender.
This was not your typical Newcomer vs. the Champion match up you would expect. Vendetta found herself on the end of some tough holds, and gave up more style points in this match then all of season two combined. The Python shows great promise!
title: Vendetta (13-3) Ranked 1st
